01:50.460 --> 01:53.130
我现在眼睛都没法从你身上移开了
I'm kind of having a hard time not looking at you now.

01:53.140 --> 01:54.260
这样奇怪吗
Is that weird?

01:54.600 --> 01:56.290
好啦  笑笑嘛  没事的
Come on, it's okay, laugh.

01:56.300 --> 01:59.100
-先生  我有个问题  -问吧
- Sir, I have a question to ask. - Yes, please.

01:59.110 --> 02:00.840
您真跟去年《马克西姆》男士杂志的
Is it true you went 12 for 12

02:00.840 --> 02:02.780
12位封面女郎都搞过吗
with last year's Maxim cover models?

02:02.790 --> 02:05.060
