Please, no gang signs.

02:25.410 --> 02:26.860
开玩笑的  举起来吧
No, throw it up. I'm kidding.

02:26.870 --> 02:28.730
和平  我爱和平
Yeah, peace. I love peace.

02:28.890 --> 02:30.140
要是和平了我就没生意了
I'd be out of a job with peace.

02:30.150 --> 02:32.560
快点啊  快按键拍照
Come on. Hurry up. Just click it.

02:32.570 --> 02:34.140
