But if I were Tony,

06:25.350 --> 06:28.270
我会告诉你们我感到多么荣幸
I would tell you how honoured I feel

06:28.280 --> 06:31.550
以及接受如此高的荣誉
and what a joy it is to receive this very

06:31.550 --> 06:33.410
是多么令人开心
prestigious award.

06:33.420 --> 06:34.580
托尼  要知道
Tony, you know...

06:35.050 --> 06:38.870
