06:52.780 --> 06:55.340
糟糕  是他们叫你来的吗
Oh, no! Did they rope you into this?

06:55.350 --> 06:56.520
没谁叫我做什么
Nobody roped me into anything!

06:56.530 --> 06:57.710
-对不起  -但他们跟我说
- I'm so sorry. - But they told me that

06:57.720 --> 07:00.290
如果由我来给你颁奖  你会倍感荣幸
if I presented you with an award, you'd be deeply honoured.

07:00.300 --> 07:02.310
