您对此有何看法
What do you say to that?

07:54.860 --> 07:56.790
荒唐  我又不会画画
Absolutely ridiculous. I don't paint.

07:56.800 --> 07:58.510
那您怎么看待你的其他外号
And what do you say to your other nickname?

07:58.520 --> 07:59.770
"死亡商人"
"The Merchant of Death"?

07:59.780 --> 08:00.860
这不算坏
That's not bad.

08:01.780 --> 08:04.010
我猜猜  伯克利毕业的
Let me guess. Berkeley?

08:04.180 --> 08:05.420
其实是布朗大学
Brown, actually.

08:05.430 --> 08:07.800
布朗大学小姐
Well, Ms Brown,

08:08.280 --> 08:10.400
这是个不完美的世界  但我们只有这个世界
it's an imperfect world, but it's the only one we've got.

08:10.410 --> 08:11.140
我向你保证
I guarantee you,

08:11.140 --> 08:13.120
如果哪天再不需要武器来维护和平了
the day weapons are no longer needed to keep the peace,

08:13.130 --> 08:15.560
我会开始为婴儿医院制造建材的
I'll start making bricks and beams for baby hospitals.

08:15.570 --> 08:16.640
这段话常练吗
Rehearse that much?

08:16.650 --> 08:18.390
每晚睡觉前都会对着镜子说
Every night in front of the mirror before bedtime.

08:18.400 --> 08:20.790
-看出来了  -我想让你亲眼见识一下
- I can see that. - I'd like to show you first-hand.

08:20.800 --> 08:23.180
