All I want is a serious answer.

08:23.190 --> 08:25.380
好吧  说严肃的  我老爸有个理论
Okay, here's serious. My old man had a philosophy,

08:25.390 --> 08:27.980
"和平就是比对方的棍子大"
"Peace means having a bigger stick than the other guy."

08:27.990 --> 08:30.350
