12:13.990 --> 12:17.930
-嗯  -很有品味  谢谢  斯塔克先生
- Yeah. - Very tasteful. Thank you, Mr Stark.

12:17.940 --> 12:19.570
不客气  波茨小姐
You're welcome, Miss Potts.

12:23.330 --> 12:24.320
好了
Okay.

12:42.710 --> 12:46.460
你挺厉害  我刚刚以为甩掉你了
You're good. I thought I lost you back there.

12:46.930 --> 12:48.000
是这样  先生
You did, sir.

12:49.380 --> 12:51.020
我不得不抄穆赫兰道的捷径
I had to cut across Mulholland.

12:51.250 --> 12:52.580
被我甩掉了吧
I got you. I got you.

12:52.590 --> 12:54.150
你什么毛病
What's wrong with you?

12:54.160 --> 12:55.780
-怎么了  -三小时
- What? - Three hours.

12:55.790 --> 12:57.820
忙着接受《名利场》的采访呢
I got caught doing a piece for Vanity Fair.

12:57.830 --> 13:00.000
三小时  你让我在这儿站了三小时
For three hours. For three hours you got me standing here.

13:00.010 --> 13:02.470
现在等你了  走吧  快来
Waiting on you now. Let's go. Come on.

13:03.170 --> 13:05.380
起飞  开始吧
Wheels up! Rock and roll!

13:13.270 --> 13:15.880
-你看什么呢  鸭嘴兽  -没事
- What you reading, platypus? - Nothing.

13:15.890 --> 13:18.190
得了  酸糖娃  别生气嘛
Come on, sour patch. Don't be mad.

13:18.200 --> 13:21.090
我说了  我没生气  我不在乎  好吗
I told you, I'm not mad. I'm indifferent, okay?

13:21.100 --> 13:22.550
-我都道歉了  -早上好  斯塔克先生
- I said I was sorry. - Good morning, Mr Stark.

13:22.560 --> 13:23.550
你不用向我道歉
