13:23.560 --> 13:24.880
-我是你的哥们  -我都跟他道歉了  但他
- I'm your man. - I told him I was sorry, but he...

13:24.890 --> 13:26.690
-我现在就是不在乎了  -热毛巾要吗
- I'm just indifferent right now. - Hot towel?

13:26.700 --> 13:29.090
你不尊重自己  所以我知道你不尊重我
You don't respect yourself, so I know you don't respect me.

13:29.100 --> 13:30.200
-我尊重你  -我就是你的保姆
- I respect you. - I'm just your babysitter.

13:30.210 --> 13:33.170
如果你需要换尿布了  谢谢
So, when you need your diaper changed... Thank you.

13:33.180 --> 13:35.720
就告诉我  我去给你拿奶瓶  好吗
Let me know and I'll get you a bottle, okay?

13:36.040 --> 13:37.140
加热下清酒  好吗
Heat up the sake, will you?

13:37.150 --> 13:38.630
-多谢提醒我  -我不是说
- Thanks for reminding me. - No, I'm not talking...

13:38.640 --> 13:40.500
我们不喝酒  我们在工作
We're not drinking. We're working right now.

13:40.510 --> 13:42.830
-吃生鱼片一定要配清酒  -你根本就是
- You can't have sashimi without sake. - You are constitutionally

13:42.840 --> 13:44.810
做不到负责任
incapable of being responsible.

13:44.820 --> 13:46.120
不喝酒才不负责
It would be irresponsible not to drink.

13:46.130 --> 13:47.150
不过是一杯睡前酒
I'm just talking about a nightcap.

13:47.160 --> 13:48.380
热清酒
Hot sake?

13:48.390 --> 13:49.230
好  来两杯  谢谢
Yes, two, please.

13:49.240 --> 13:51.810
不  我不喝  我不要
No. I'm not drinking. I don't want any.

13:51.820 --> 13:53.180
我就这意思
That's what I'm talking about.

13:53.190 --> 13:56.180
我早上起床  穿上军服
When I get up in the morning and I'm putting on my uniform,

13:56.190 --> 13:58.290
知道我认得什么吗
you know what I recognise?

13:58.300 --> 13:59.530
我在镜子里能看到
I see in that mirror that

13:59.540 --> 14:03.450
每一个穿着这军服的人都会照应我
every person that's got this uniform on got my back!

14:03.460 --> 14:05.820
知道吗  我跟你不一样  我不适合
Hey, you know what? I'm not like you. I'm not cut out...

14:05.830 --> 14:07.900
不  你不非得像我一样
No, no. You don't have to be like me!

14:07.910 --> 14:09.310
但你远不止现在的你自己
But you're more than what you are.

14:09.320 --> 14:11.380
抱歉  我现在有点无法集中精神
Can you excuse me if I'm a bit distracted here?

14:11.390 --> 14:14.890
不  你现在不能不集中精神  听我说
No! You can't be distracted right now! Listen to me!

14:18.370 --> 14:21.330
<b>阿富汗  巴格兰空军基地</b>

14:31.130 --> 14:32.060
将军
General.

14:32.150 --> 14:33.530
欢迎  斯塔克先生
Welcome, Mr Stark.

14:34.190 --> 14:35.980
我们很期待您的武器展示
We look forward to your weapons presentation.

14:35.990 --> 14:36.940
谢谢
Thanks.

14:38.730 --> 14:41.810
被恐惧和被尊敬  哪个更好
Is it better to be feared or respected?

14:41.820 --> 14:45.140
要我说  两个都要算过分吗
I say, is it too much to ask for both?

14:45.830 --> 14:48.750
因此  我谦卑地献上斯塔克工业
With that in mind, I humbly present the crown jewel

14:48.760 --> 14:50.660
自由系列的旗舰产品
of Stark Industries' Freedom Line.

14:50.670 --> 14:51.700
这是第一个融入了
It's the first missile system

14:51.710 --> 14:54.810
我们的专利冲击科技的导弹系统
to incorporate our proprietary repulsor technology.

14:54.820 --> 14:58.890
人说最好的武器是不需要使用的武器
They say the best weapon is one you never have to fire.

14:58.900 --> 15:00.920
我尊重地表示不同意
I respectfully disagree.

15:00.930 --> 15:05.220
我更喜欢你只需要使用一次的武器
I prefer the weapon you only have to fire once.

15:05.230 --> 15:08.500
我老爸就这么做  美国就这么做
That's how Dad did it. That's how America does it.

15:09.130 --> 15:11.470
而且到目前一直挺成功
And it's worked out pretty well so far.

15:11.480 --> 15:12.820
找个借口
Find an excuse

15:12.830 --> 15:16.250
发射一次这玩意  我亲自担保
to let one of these off the chain, and I personally guarantee you

15:16.260 --> 15:19.690
坏蛋再也不会想从洞里爬出来了
the bad guys won't even want to come out of their caves.

15:38.220 --> 15:42.700
供您参考  耶利哥
For your consideration, the Jericho.

15:53.360 --> 15:54.290
每笔超过五亿的交易
I'll be throwing one of these in

15:54.300 --> 15:56.840
我送一个这个
with every purchase of 500 million or more.

15:56.850 --> 15:57.960
敬和平
To peace!

15:59.560 --> 16:01.790
-托尼  -奥比  你怎么起来了
- Tony. - Obie, what are you doing up?

16:01.800 --> 16:04.230
不清楚情况我睡不着  展示得怎么样
I couldn't sleep till I found out how it went. How'd it go?

16:04.240 --> 16:06.610
很好  看来圣诞节要提前了
It went great. Looks like it's gonna be an early Christmas.

16:07.050 --> 16:10.220
好样的  伙计  明天见了
Way to go, my boy! I'll see you tomorrow, yeah?

16:10.230 --> 16:11.440
你怎么没穿我送你的睡衣
Why aren't you wearing those pyjamas I got you?

16:11.450 --> 16:13.000
晚安  托尼
Good night, Tony.

16:14.680 --> 16:17.150
-托尼  -抱歉  这辆车是"欢乐马"
- Hey, Tony. - I'm sorry, this is the "Fun-vee."

16:17.160 --> 16:19.020
"悍无聊马"在后面
The "Hum-drum-vee" Is back there.

16:19.510 --> 16:21.980
-好样的  -基地见
- Nice job. - See you back at base.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.640
我劝你别那么做
I wouldn't do that if I were you.

18:07.790 --> 18:09.440
你对我做了什么
What the hell did you do to me?

18:10.420 --> 18:11.560
我做了什么
What I did?

18:13.140 --> 18:15.250
我做的事是救你命
What I did is to save your life.

18:15.260 --> 18:18.750
我已经尽力移除了很多弹片  但还剩不少
I removed all the shrapnel I could, but there's a lot left,

18:18.760 --> 18:21.100
而且它们都在往你的房隔去
and it's headed into your atrial septum.

18:21.380 --> 18:22.590
想看看吗
Here, want to see?

18:23.890 --> 18:26.900
我留了纪念品  看看吧
I have a souvenir. Take a look.

18:29.400 --> 18:31.800
我在我的村子里见过不少这样的伤
I've seen many wounds like that in my village.

18:31.810 --> 18:34.320
我们称他们为将死行尸
We call them the walking dead

18:34.330 --> 18:35.490
因为大概要一周
because it takes about a week

18:35.500 --> 18:37.440
弹片才会进入重要器官
for the barbs to reach the vital organs.

18:37.450 --> 18:41.110
-这是什么  -那是块电磁铁
- What is this? - That is an electromagnet,

18:41.120 --> 18:43.270
连在了汽车电池上
hooked up to a car battery,

18:43.280 --> 18:45.980
它在阻止弹片进入你的心脏
and it's keeping the shrapnel from entering your heart.

18:54.410 --> 18:56.900
没错  笑笑
That's right. Smile.

18:58.200 --> 19:02.440
我们见过一次  在伯尔尼的一场科技大会上
We met once, you know, at a technical conference in Bern.

19:02.750 --> 19:05.830
-我不记得了  -当然了
- I don't remember. - No, you wouldn't.

19:05.840 --> 19:08.890
如果我喝得那么醉  肯定站都站不直
If I had been that drunk, I wouldn't have been able to stand,

19:08.900 --> 19:12.340
更别说就集成电路发表讲话了
much less give a lecture on integrated circuits.

19:12.350 --> 19:13.460
我们在哪
Where are we?

19:15.430 --> 19:17.730
快起来  起来
Come on, stand up. Stand up!

19:18.130 --> 19:20.510
学我的样子做
Just do as I do.

19:21.050 --> 19:22.580
把手举起来
Come on, put your hands up.

19:24.950 --> 19:26.440
那是我的枪  他们怎么弄到的
Those are my guns. How did they get my guns?

19:26.450 --> 19:28.690
你听懂了没  学我的样子做
Do you understand me? Do as I do.

19:49.310 --> 19:53.640
他说"欢迎  托尼·斯塔克  美国历史上
He says, "Welcome, Tony Stark, the most famous mass murderer

19:53.650 --> 19:55.540
最著名的大屠杀犯"
in the history of America."

19:58.790 --> 19:59.920
他很荣幸
He is honoured.

20:02.830 --> 20:04.880
他要你给他建导弹
He wants you to build the missile.

20:06.020 --> 20:08.840
你展示的那个耶利哥导弹
The Jericho missile that you demonstrated.

20:12.000 --> 20:12.970
这个
This one.

20:18.190 --> 20:19.350
我拒绝
I refuse.

20:30.000 --> 20:30.940
托尼
Tony!

21:11.080 --> 21:15.040
<b>斯塔克工业</b>

21:20.850 --> 21:23.300
他问你觉得怎么样
He wants to know what you think.

21:24.220 --> 21:26.230
我觉得你有好多我的武器
I think you got a lot of my weapons.

21:35.030 --> 21:36.770
他说他们有你需要
He says they have everything

21:36.780 --> 21:39.270
拿来建造耶利哥的一切
you need to build the Jericho missile.

21:39.800 --> 21:42.060
他要你列出材料清单
He wants you to make the list of materials.

21:45.490 --> 21:47.950
他说要你立刻开始动手
He says for you to start working immediately,

21:47.960 --> 21:51.070
你做好了  他就放了你
and when you're done, he will set you free.

21:54.530 --> 21:57.630
-不  他不会的  -是啊
- No, he won't. - No, he won't.

22:10.810 --> 22:12.780
他们肯定在找你  斯塔克
I'm sure they're looking for you, Stark.

22:13.440 --> 22:16.330
但在这些山里  他们是找不到你的
But they will never find you in these mountains.

22:19.820 --> 22:22.160
你刚刚看到一切
Look, what you just saw,

22:22.760 --> 22:24.980
那就是你的遗产  斯塔克
that is your legacy, Stark.

22:26.420 --> 22:29.920
你一生的心血  落在那些杀人犯手里
Your life's work, in the hands of those murderers.

22:29.930 --> 22:31.520
你想这样死去吗
Is that how you want to go out?

22:32.700 --> 22:35.500
这就是伟大的托尼·斯塔克的
Is this the last act of defiance

22:35.500 --> 22:37.950
最后反抗吗
of the great Tony Stark?

22:38.380 --> 22:40.080
还是说你要想想办法
Or are you going to do something about it?

22:40.090 --> 22:41.220
我何必还要做点什么
Why should I do anything?

22:41.230 --> 22:45.230
他们无论如何都会杀了你  杀了我
They're going to kill me, you, either way.

22:45.240 --> 22:47.590
就算不  我大概也活不过一周
And if they don't, I'll probably be dead in a week.

22:48.540 --> 22:49.830
那么
Well, then,

22:50.550 --> 22:53.100
这一周就对你至关重要了吧
this is a very important week for you, isn't it?

22:56.390 --> 22:57.620
如果这里要做我的工作站
If this is going to be my work station,

22:57.630 --> 22:59.410
我要灯火通明  这个竖好
I want it well-lit. I want these up.

23:00.000 --> 23:02.950
我需要焊接工具  乙炔和丙烷的都行
I need welding gear. I don't care if it's acetylene or propane.

23:02.960 --> 23:03.950
我需要焊接工作台
I need a soldering station.

23:03.960 --> 23:05.360
头盔  护目镜
I need helmets. I'm gonna need goggles.

23:05.370 --> 23:09.230
我还要熔炼杯  两组精密工具
I would like a smelting cup. I need two sets of precision tools.

23:12.160 --> 23:16.540
<b>斯塔克工业</b>

23:22.030 --> 23:24.540
-你说多少种语言  -好多种
- How many languages do you speak? - A lot.

23:24.550 --> 23:26.700
但看来在这里还是不够用
But apparently, not enough for this place.

23:27.310 --> 23:29.520
他们说阿拉伯语  乌尔都语
They speak Arabic, Urdu,

23:29.520 --> 23:31.220
达里语  帕施图语
dari, Pashto,

23:31.230 --> 23:33.230
蒙古语  波斯语  俄语
Mongolian, Farsi, Russian.

23:34.020 --> 23:35.400
他们是什么人
Who are these people?

23:35.410 --> 23:38.930
他们是你的忠实顾客  先生
They are your loyal customers, sir.

23:38.940 --> 23:41.340
他们自称"十戒组织"
They call themselves the Ten Rings.

23:50.410 --> 23:51.890
如果你告诉我你的计划
You know, we might be more productive

23:51.900 --> 23:54.260
我们的动作可能会更快
if you include me in the planning process.

24:03.220 --> 24:05.610
好吧  我们不需要这个
Okay, we don't need this.

24:07.520 --> 24:08.480
那是什么
What is that?

24:10.490 --> 24:13.300
钯  0.15克
That's palladium, 0.15 grammes.

24:13.450 --> 24:14.710
我们需要至少1.6
We need at least 1.6,

24:14.720 --> 24:16.740
你去把另外11个拆了吧
so why don't you go break down the other 11?

24:20.100 --> 24:21.150
他在干什么
What's he doing?

24:22.020 --> 24:23.290
干活儿
Working.

24:33.560 --> 24:36.450
小心  我们只有一次机会
Careful. Careful, we only get one shot at this.

24:36.550 --> 24:39.550
放心  我手很稳
Relax. I have steady hands.

24:40.150 --> 24:41.940
要不你怎么会还活着
Why do you think you're still alive?

24:48.960 --> 24:52.580
-怎么称呼你  -我叫殷森
- What do I call you? - My name is Yinsen.

24:52.910 --> 24:55.020
殷森  认识你很高兴
Yinsen. Nice to meet you.

24:56.160 --> 24:57.830
我也很高兴认识你
Nice to meet you, too.

25:38.040 --> 25:40.700
那看上去不像耶利哥导弹
That doesn't look like a Jericho missile.

25:40.710 --> 25:43.490
因为那是个迷你方舟反应堆
That's because it's a miniaturised arc reactor.

25:44.190 --> 25:46.810
我家里有个大的给我的工厂供电
I got a big one powering my factory at home.

25:47.390 --> 25:49.320
这应该足以阻止弹片进入我的心脏
It should keep the shrapnel out of my heart.

25:50.120 --> 25:51.870
但它能产生什么
But what could it generate?

25:51.880 --> 25:54.930
如果我没算错  我通常不会算错
If my math is right, and it always is,

25:54.940 --> 25:56.970
每秒能产生3千兆焦耳
three gigajoules per second.

25:56.980 --> 25:59.780
那足以让你的心跳50辈子
That could run your heart for 50 lifetimes.

26:00.790 --> 26:02.790
或者让什么大玩意跑15分钟
Or something big for 15 minutes.

26:11.700 --> 26:14.940
-这是我们逃离的方法  -是什么
- This is our ticket out of here. - What is it?

26:16.400 --> 26:18.000
摊平了看
Flatten them out and look.

26:24.670 --> 26:26.170
厉害
Impressive.

26:52.370 --> 26:53.410
很好
Good.

26:54.340 --> 26:57.350
下得好
Good roll. Good roll.

26:57.850 --> 26:59.520
你还没跟我说你是哪里人
You still haven't told me where you're from.

26:59.780 --> 27:02.620
我来自一个叫科米拉的小镇
I'm from a small town called Gulmira.

27:03.040 --> 27:06.430
-那里其实很不错  -有家人吗
- It's actually a nice place. - Got a family?

27:06.440 --> 27:10.950
有  等我离开这里  就能见到他们
Yes, and I will see them when I leave here.

27:11.640 --> 27:12.780
你呢  斯塔克
And you, Stark?

27:17.320 --> 27:19.870
-没有  -没有吗
- No. - No?

27:21.190 --> 27:23.790
你是个拥有一切的人
So you're a man who has everything

27:24.570 --> 27:25.760
却一无所有
and nothing.

28:11.620 --> 28:14.870
看上去完全不像照片上的东西
It doesn't look anything like the picture.

28:14.880 --> 28:16.580
或许是改装过了
Maybe it's been modified.

28:16.590 --> 28:17.650
尾翼不对
The tail is wrong.

28:17.660 --> 28:19.100
就是倒过来了
It's just backwards.

29:04.340 --> 29:05.480
放松
Relax.

29:14.560 --> 29:15.860
弓和箭
The bow and arrow

