What the hell is this?

01:17:11.830 --> 01:17:13.210
打死这家伙
Shoot this dog.

01:17:13.860 --> 01:17:15.410
你们这群没用的东西
You're all incompetent.

01:17:18.850 --> 01:17:20.020
