No, sir, they were using human shields.

01:19:30.120 --> 01:19:31.240
我们没获得批准
We never got the green light.

01:19:31.240 --> 01:19:32.850
给我接国务院  肯定是他们搞的
Put me through to State. They're going to be all over this.

01:19:32.850 --> 01:19:34.390
调出显示
Get those monitors up!

01:19:34.880 --> 01:19:35.870
发现不明物体
We got a bogey!

01:19:36.190 --> 01:19:38.450
-不是空军  -接通中情局了吗
- Wasn't Air Force! - We got the CIA on the line?

01:19:38.450 --> 01:19:40.580
