and cross-referenced with all known databases.

01:20:01.270 --> 01:20:02.080
毫无发现
We have nothing.

01:20:02.080 --> 01:20:04.230
当地有高空监控吗
Any high altitude surveillance in the region?

01:20:04.230 --> 01:20:06.050
当地有空中早期预警和全球鹰
We got an AWAC and a Global Hawk in the area.

01:20:06.050 --> 01:20:07.730
这玩意是突然冒出来的吗
So this thing just appeared out of nowhere?

01:20:07.730 --> 01:20:09.300
