Yeah, well, I need your help right now.

01:20:39.460 --> 01:20:40.820
天道好轮回啊
It's funny how that works, huh?

01:20:40.820 --> 01:20:41.920
是啊  是这样
Yeah. Speaking of funny,

01:20:41.920 --> 01:20:44.270
有个武器站刚被炸毁了
we've got a weapons depot that was just blown up

01:20:44.270 --> 01:20:46.110
离你当初被囚的地方只有几公里
a few clicks from where you were being held captive.

01:20:46.110 --> 01:20:47.880
那里挺危险的
Well, that's a hot spot.

01:20:47.880 --> 01:20:50.320
似乎是有人插手替你完成了工作  是吧
Sounds like someone stepped in and did your job for you, huh?

01:20:50.320 --> 01:20:51.580
你为什么气喘吁吁的  托尼
Why do you sound out of breath, Tony?

01:20:51.580 --> 01:20:52.830
我没有  我在峡谷里慢跑呢
I'm not, I was justjogging in the canyon.

01:20:52.830 --> 01:20:54.730
-你不是在开车吗  -是啊  我开车
- I thought you were driving. - Right, I was driving

01:20:54.730 --> 01:20:56.530
到了峡谷  然后去慢跑
to the canyon, where I'm going to jog.

01:20:56.530 --> 01:20:57.730
你在那一带真没有什么
You sure you don't have any tech

01:20:57.730 --> 01:20:59.110
我应该知道的东西吗
in that area I should know about?

01:20:59.120 --> 01:21:00.740
-没有  -发现不明物体了
- Nope! - Bogey spotted!

01:21:00.740 --> 01:21:02.070
鞭子战机  正在前往
Whiplash, come in hot.

01:21:02.070 --> 01:21:03.950
很好  因为我眼前就有个东西
Okay, good, 'cause I'm staring at one right now,

01:21:03.950 --> 01:21:06.000
马上要被炸飞了
and it's about to be blown to kingdom come.

01:21:07.240 --> 01:21:08.480
我该撤了
That's my exit.

01:21:14.000 --> 01:21:15.330
战情室  这里是鞭子一号
Ballroom, this is Whiplash One.

01:21:15.330 --> 01:21:17.030
我看到不明物体了
I've got the bogey in my sights.

01:21:17.600 --> 01:21:19.230
鞭子一号  那是什么玩意
Whiplash One, what is it?

01:21:19.230 --> 01:21:20.610
我不知道
I've got no idea.

01:21:20.610 --> 01:21:23.070
-能进行无线电联络吗  -无反应  长官
- You have radio contact? - Non responsive, sir.

01:21:23.070 --> 01:21:24.700
那你可以交火
Then you are clear to engage.

01:21:25.930 --> 01:21:27.060
<b>超音速飞行</b>

01:21:26.190 --> 01:21:27.190
启动
Hit it.

01:21:32.020 --> 01:21:34.410
不明物体刚进入了超音速  我锁定了
That bogey just went supersonic. I got a lock!

01:21:39.000 --> 01:21:41.570
-导弹来袭  -照明弹
- lnbound missile. - Flares!

01:21:44.030 --> 01:21:46.000
等等  不明物体调用了照明弹
Wait a second. Bogey deployed flares!

01:22:00.990 --> 01:22:02.060
展开襟翼
Deploy flaps!

01:22:03.480 --> 01:22:04.410
我去
Holy!

01:22:04.720 --> 01:22:06.280
那玩意从雷达上消失了  长官
That thing just jumped off the radar, sir.

01:22:06.290 --> 01:22:07.930
卫星盯丢了
The sat visual has been lost.

01:22:08.040 --> 01:22:09.790
那绝不是无人机
No way that's a UAV.

01:22:09.850 --> 01:22:10.870
是什么
What is it?

01:22:10.870 --> 01:22:12.300
我什么都看不到
I can't see anything.

01:22:12.580 --> 01:22:14.800
不管是什么  刚刚已经死了
Whatever it was, it just bought the farm.

01:22:15.580 --> 01:22:17.510
不明物体应该已经被处理掉了  长官
I think bogey's been handled, sir.

01:22:27.560 --> 01:22:29.340
-喂  -罗德  是我
- Hello? - Hi, Rhodey, it's me.

01:22:29.340 --> 01:22:31.170
-谁  -抱歉  确实是我
- It's who? - I'm sorry, it is me.

01:22:31.170 --> 01:22:32.510
你问了  你问的那个就是我
You asked. What you were asking about is me.

01:22:32.510 --> 01:22:34.100
瞧  这不是游戏
No, see, this isn't a game.

01:22:34.100 --> 01:22:37.340
你不能把平民装备飞入我的活动战区
You do not send civilian equipment into my active war zone.

01:22:37.340 --> 01:22:39.560
-你懂不懂  -不是一件装备
- You understand that? - This is not a piece of equipment.

01:22:39.560 --> 01:22:42.200
我在里面呢  是件战衣  那是我
I'm in it. It's a suit. It's me!

01:22:42.350 --> 01:22:43.960
罗德  你查到什么了吗
Rhodey, you got anything for me?

01:22:45.830 --> 01:22:48.770
-标记位置  回基地  -收到  战情室
- Mark your position and return to base. - Roger that, Ballroom.

01:22:51.540 --> 01:22:52.610
在你底下
On your belly!

01:22:52.610 --> 01:22:54.710
像是个人
lt looks like a man!

01:22:54.850 --> 01:22:57.410
甩掉他  翻滚
Shake him off! Roll! Roll!

01:23:05.520 --> 01:23:06.970
我被打中了
I'm hit! I'm hit!

01:23:06.970 --> 01:23:08.620
确认  他被击中了
It's confirmed. He has been hit.

01:23:13.220 --> 01:23:14.800
跳伞
Punch out! Punch out!

01:23:21.680 --> 01:23:23.380
鞭子一号坠机
Whiplash One down.

01:23:23.550 --> 01:23:25.200
鞭子二号  看到降落伞了吗
Whiplash Two, do you see a chute?

01:23:25.200 --> 01:23:27.470
没有  没有降落伞
Negative! No chute, no chute!

01:23:33.020 --> 01:23:34.430
