My chute's jammed!

01:23:40.260 --> 01:23:42.530
长官  我看到不明物体了
Sir, I've got a visual on the bogey.

01:23:42.730 --> 01:23:43.930
鞭子二号  再次出击
Whiplash Two, reengage.

01:23:43.930 --> 01:23:45.750
如果能击落  就击落
If you get a clear shot, you take it.

01:23:47.920 --> 01:23:49.680
少校  我们都不知道那是什么
Major, we don't even know what we're shooting at.

01:23:49.680 --> 01:23:50.340
让猛禽回来
Call off the Raptors.

01:23:50.350 --> 01:23:51.730
那玩意刚在合法禁飞区内
That thing just took out an F- 22

01:23:51.730 --> 01:23:53.180
击落了一架F22
inside a legal no fly zone!

01:23:53.180 --> 01:23:55.870
鞭子二号  如果能击落  就击落
Whiplash Two, if you have a clear shot, take it!

01:23:55.870 --> 01:23:58.330
你又被锁定了  进行躲避操作
You've been reengaged. Execute evasive manoeuvre.

01:23:58.330 --> 01:23:59.260
继续飞
Keep going!

01:24:07.230 --> 01:24:09.290
降落伞打开
Good chute! Good chute!

01:24:16.920 --> 01:24:19.760
-托尼  你还在吗  -谢谢了
- Tony, you still there? - Hey, thanks.

01:24:19.760 --> 01:24:22.370
天呐  你个疯子
Oh, my God, you crazy son of a bitch.

01:24:23.190 --> 01:24:25.160
你欠我架飞机  你知道吧
You owe me a plane. You know that, right?

01:24:26.450 --> 01:24:28.240
严格讲  是他撞了我
Yeah, well, technically, he hit me.

01:24:28.240 --> 01:24:30.210
你要过来看看我在做什么吗
Now are you going to come by and see what I'm working on?

01:24:30.210 --> 01:24:33.360
不要  我知道得越少越好
No, no, no, no, no, no, the less I know, the better.

01:24:33.660 --> 01:24:35.320
