It's not that simple.

01:24:40.460 --> 01:24:42.370
昨天一架猛禽F22
An unfortunate training exercise

01:24:42.370 --> 01:24:45.480
在演练中不幸发生事故
involving an F-22 Raptor occurred yesterday.

01:24:45.960 --> 01:24:49.220
庆幸的是  飞行员并未受伤
I am pleased to report that the pilot was not injured.

01:24:49.450 --> 01:24:53.200
至于科米拉村庄意料之外的局势反转
As for the unexpected turn of events on the ground in Gulmira,

01:24:53.440 --> 01:24:57.060
是谁或是什么进行了干预  我们尚不清楚
it is still unclear who or what intervened,

01:24:57.060 --> 01:24:58.330
但我可以保证
but I can assure you that

01:24:58.330 --> 01:25:01.300
此事与美国政府无关
the United States government was not involved.

01:25:06.250 --> 01:25:07.950
的确很贴身  先生
It is a tight fit, sir.

01:25:09.130 --> 01:25:11.980
先生  您越是扭动  就会越疼
Sir, the more you struggle, the more this is going to hurt.

01:25:12.080 --> 01:25:13.720
温柔点  这是我第一次
Be gentle. This is my first time.

01:25:14.950 --> 01:25:16.910
我设计它能脱下来的  所以
I designed this to come off, so...

01:25:19.080 --> 01:25:20.410
