I really should be able to...

01:25:21.360 --> 01:25:22.980
请尽量不要动  先生
Please, try not to move, sir.

01:25:24.300 --> 01:25:25.720
怎么回事啊
What's going on here?

01:25:31.140 --> 01:25:31.790
承认吧
Let's face it.

01:25:31.790 --> 01:25:33.840
这不是你撞见我做的最糟糕的事
This is not the worst thing you've caught me doing.

01:25:35.790 --> 01:25:37.350
那是弹孔吗
Are those bullet holes?

01:26:05.170 --> 01:26:06.150
欢迎
Welcome.

01:26:09.720 --> 01:26:11.550
