Compliments of Tony Stark.

01:26:12.760 --> 01:26:14.360
如果你当初按计划杀了他
If you'd killed him when you were supposed to,

01:26:14.360 --> 01:26:15.960
也不会把脸烧掉了
you'd still have a face.

01:26:16.460 --> 01:26:18.660
你给我们点小钱杀一位王子
You paid us trinkets to kill a prince.

01:26:18.710 --> 01:26:20.260
带我去看武器
Show me the weapon.

01:26:21.670 --> 01:26:25.270
来吧  让守卫留在外面
Come. Leave your guards outside.

01:26:41.970 --> 01:26:44.180
