Get me Major Allen. Scramble the jets!

01:47:49.160 --> 01:47:52.260
不必了  各位  只是演练
Not necessary, people. Just a training exercise.

01:47:52.560 --> 01:47:53.470
是  长官
Yes, sir.

01:48:01.370 --> 01:48:02.850
只剩13%的电力了  先生
Thirteen percent power, sir.

01:48:02.850 --> 01:48:03.670
继续爬升
Climb!

01:48:07.470 --> 01:48:09.490
-11%  -继续飞
