你的点子很棒  托尼
You had a great idea, Tony,

01:48:31.300 --> 01:48:34.190
但我的战衣在各方面都更先进
but my suit is more advanced in every way!

01:48:34.800 --> 01:48:36.560
你怎么解决结冰问题的
How'd you solve the icing problem?

01:48:36.950 --> 01:48:38.270
什么结冰问题
Icing problem?

01:48:40.690 --> 01:48:42.130
最好查看一下
Might want to look into it.

01:48:54.640 --> 01:48:55.780
2%
Two percent.

01:48:58.100 --> 01:49:00.730
现在在使用紧急备用电力
We are now running on emergency backup power.

01:49:12.630 --> 01:49:16.210
-波茨  -托尼  天呐  你没事吧
- Potts! - Tony! Oh, my God, are you okay?

01:49:16.220 --> 01:49:17.550
我快没电了
I'm almost out of power.

01:49:17.560 --> 01:49:19.860
我得脱掉战衣  我就过去
I've got to get out of this thing. I'll be right there.

01:49:20.390 --> 01:49:21.650
想得美
Nice try!

01:49:34.710 --> 01:49:36.270
武器状态
Weapons status?

01:49:36.460 --> 01:49:39.000
冲击系统下线  导弹下线
Repulsors offline. Missiles offline.

01:49:42.910 --> 01:49:43.910
燃烧弹
Flares!

01:49:52.870 --> 01:49:55.090
真聪明  托尼
Very clever, Tony.

01:50:00.290 --> 01:50:02.830
-波茨  -托尼
- Potts? - Tony!

01:50:02.830 --> 01:50:03.410
这样不行
This isn't working.

01:50:03.410 --> 01:50:06.040
我们得过载反应堆  炸碎屋顶
We're going to have to overload the reactor and blast the roof.

01:50:06.290 --> 01:50:09.180
-你要怎么做到  -你来做
- Well, how are you going to do that? - You're going to do it.

01:50:09.200 --> 01:50:11.720
去中央控制台  打开所有电路
Go to the central console, open up all the circuits.

01:50:11.720 --> 01:50:13.020
等我撤离了屋顶  就告诉你
When I get clear of the roof, I'll let you know.

01:50:13.020 --> 01:50:15.420
你就按下主旁路按钮
You're going to hit the master bypass button.

01:50:16.010 --> 01:50:17.670
上面的一切都会被烧毁
It's going to fry everything up here.

01:50:19.500 --> 01:50:21.840
好  我这就进去
Okay. I'm going in now.

01:50:21.850 --> 01:50:24.990
一定等我离开屋顶的  我给你争取点时间
Make sure you wait till I clear the roof. I'll buy you some time.

01:50:34.650 --> 01:50:36.100
这个看上去挺重要
This looks important!

01:50:57.400 --> 01:50:59.870
我一向不怎么喜欢这种玩意
I never had a taste for this sort of thing,

01:51:00.300 --> 01:51:04.570
但我得承认  我非常喜欢这件战衣
but I must admit, I'm deeply enjoying the suit!

01:51:12.640 --> 01:51:15.120
你可算超常发挥了  托尼
You finally outdid yourself, Tony!

01:51:17.620 --> 01:51:19.700
你会让你父亲自豪的
You'd have made your father proud!

01:51:24.650 --> 01:51:26.740
准备好了  托尼  快离开屋顶
It's ready, Tony! Get off the roof!

01:51:46.640 --> 01:51:48.130
托尼
Tony!

01:51:49.140 --> 01:51:50.950
真是讽刺  托尼
How ironic, Tony!

01:51:52.730 --> 01:51:54.830
你想让世界上不再有武器
Trying to rid the world of weapons,

01:51:55.430 --> 01:51:57.650
却发明了最棒的武器
you gave it its best one ever!

01:51:57.650 --> 01:51:59.970
-派珀  -现在
- Pepper! - And now

01:52:01.680 --> 01:52:03.500
我要拿它杀了你
I'm going to kill you with it!

01:52:06.730 --> 01:52:10.720
-你扯掉了我的瞄准系统  -按按钮
- You ripped out my targeting system! - Time to hit the button!

01:52:10.720 --> 01:52:14.730
-你叫我别按的  -别动  你个小混蛋
- You told me not to! - Hold still, you little prick!

01:52:16.590 --> 01:52:19.540
-动手吧  -你会死的
- Just do it! - You'll die!

01:52:22.390 --> 01:52:23.740
按吧
Push it!

01:53:21.250 --> 01:53:22.790
托尼
Tony!

01:53:31.410 --> 01:53:33.360
各位都拿到了昨晚斯塔克工业
You've all received the official statement of

01:53:31.490 --> 01:53:43.210
<b>詹姆斯·罗德中校  斯塔克工业事件</b>

01:53:33.360 --> 01:53:35.850
事件经过的官方报告
what occurred at Stark lndustries last night.

01:53:36.340 --> 01:53:38.140
有未经证实的报告称
There have been unconfirmed reports

01:53:38.140 --> 01:53:40.960
一件机器人原型机发生故障
that a robotic prototype malfunctioned

01:53:40.960 --> 01:53:43.630
导致方舟反应堆受损
and caused damage to the arc reactor.

01:53:44.340 --> 01:53:46.680
幸好  托尼·斯塔克的一位私人保镖
Fortunately, a member of Tony Stark's personal security staff...

01:53:44.420 --> 01:53:47.290
<b>钢铁侠是谁</b>

01:53:46.680 --> 01:53:48.630
"钢铁侠"  挺上口  挺响亮的
"Iron Man." That's kind of catchy. It's got a nice ring to it.

01:53:48.630 --> 01:53:49.980
虽然并不准确
I mean, it's not technically accurate.

01:53:49.980 --> 01:53:52.360
战衣是金钛合金
The suit's a gold-titanium alloy,

01:53:52.380 --> 01:53:55.150
但这种意向呼之欲出
but it's kind of evocative, the imagery, anyway.

01:53:55.160 --> 01:53:56.340
这是你的不在场证明
Here's your alibi.

01:53:57.700 --> 01:53:58.750
好
Okay.

01:53:58.830 --> 01:54:01.060
-你在你的游艇上  -嗯
- You were on your yacht. - Yeah.

01:54:01.060 --> 01:54:03.250
我们有港口报告证明你整晚都在阿瓦隆
We have port papers that put you in Avalon all night,

01:54:03.250 --> 01:54:05.190
还有你50位宾客的宣誓证词
and sworn statements from 50 of your guests.

01:54:05.190 --> 01:54:08.250
或许该说只有我和派珀
See, I was thinking maybe we should say it was just Pepper and me

01:54:08.250 --> 01:54:10.130
单独在岛上
alone on the island.

01:54:11.390 --> 01:54:12.740
-就是这样的  -好吧
- That's what happened. - All right.

01:54:12.740 --> 01:54:14.310
照读就行
Just read it, word for word.

01:54:16.790 --> 01:54:18.240
上面没提斯坦尼
There's nothing about Stane here.

01:54:18.860 --> 01:54:21.900
这已经处理好了  他去度假了
That's being handled. He's on vacation.

01:54:22.450 --> 01:54:24.990
小型飞机的安全记录很差
Small aircraft have such a poor safety record.

01:54:25.000 --> 01:54:27.680
但关于保镖的那套掩护说辞呢
But what about the whole cover story that it's a bodyguard?

01:54:27.680 --> 01:54:28.930
他是我的...这...
He's my... I mean, is that...

01:54:28.930 --> 01:54:30.490
这太站不住脚了吧
That's kind of flimsy, don't you think?

01:54:30.630 --> 01:54:32.690
我不是第一次做这种事了  斯塔克先生
This isn't my first rodeo, Mr Stark.

01:54:33.010 --> 01:54:34.170
按官方说辞念就行
Just stick to the official statement,

01:54:34.170 --> 01:54:36.190
很快  这一切都会过去了
and soon, this will all be behind you.

01:54:37.120 --> 01:54:39.590
你有90秒
You've got 90 seconds.

01:54:42.250 --> 01:54:43.330
科尔森特工
Agent Coulson?

01:54:44.590 --> 01:54:48.830
我想说  非常感谢你的一切帮助
I just wanted to say thank you very much for all of your help.

01:54:49.160 --> 01:54:52.170
这是我们的职责  我们还会再联系的
That's what we do. You'll be hearing from us.

01:54:52.360 --> 01:54:55.560
-你们叫国土战略  -喊我们神盾局就行
- From the Strategic Homeland... - Just call us S.H.I.E.L.D.

01:54:56.170 --> 01:54:57.130
好
Right.

01:54:58.270 --> 01:54:59.890
我们开始吧
Let's get this show on the road.

01:54:59.890 --> 01:55:02.110
其实也没那么糟
You know, it's actually not that bad.

01:55:02.110 --> 01:55:03.810
就连我都不觉得自己像钢铁侠
Even I don't think I'm Iron Man.

01:55:04.600 --> 01:55:06.240
-你不是钢铁侠  -我是
- You're not Iron Man. - Am so.

01:55:06.240 --> 01:55:08.270
-你不是  -好吧  随你
- You're not. - All right, suit yourself.

01:55:08.780 --> 01:55:10.260
如果我是钢铁侠
You know, if I were Iron Man,

01:55:10.260 --> 01:55:12.700
我会有个知道我真实身份的女友
I'd have this girlfriend who knew my true identity.

01:55:12.700 --> 01:55:13.540
而且她会很崩溃
She'd be a wreck,

01:55:13.540 --> 01:55:15.280
因为她会非常担心我会不会送命
'cause she'd always be worrying that I was going to die,

01:55:15.280 --> 01:55:17.870
但又为我的成就感到骄傲
yet so proud of the man I'd become.

01:55:17.870 --> 01:55:22.390
她会非常矛盾  而这又让她更加
She'd be wildly conflicted, which would only make her more

01:55:23.520 --> 01:55:24.450
为我疯狂了
crazy about me.

01:55:24.450 --> 01:55:26.230
你难道就没想过那晚的事吗
Tell me you never think about that night.

01:55:26.250 --> 01:55:27.790
-哪一晚  -你知道的
- What night? - You know.

01:55:31.070 --> 01:55:32.240
你是说
Are you talking about

01:55:33.100 --> 01:55:34.270
我们一起跳舞的那晚吗
the night that we danced

01:55:34.270 --> 01:55:36.750
然后我们上了屋顶
and went up on the roof,

01:55:38.430 --> 01:55:39.650
然后
and then

01:55:40.870 --> 01:55:44.120
你去楼下拿酒
you went downstairs to get me a drink,

01:55:44.120 --> 01:55:47.840
然后就撇下了我一人
and you left me there, by myself?

01:55:48.640 --> 01:55:50.340
你是说那晚吗
Is that the night you're talking about?

01:55:53.390 --> 01:55:54.520
我猜也是
Thought so.

01:55:57.110 --> 01:55:58.010
没有别的事了吧  斯塔克先生
Will that be all, Mr Stark?

01:55:58.010 --> 01:56:00.970
是的  没别的事了  波茨小姐
Yes, that will be all, Miss Potts.

01:56:00.970 --> 01:56:04.570
现在  斯塔克先生准备了一份声明
And now, Mr Stark has prepared a statement.

01:56:04.580 --> 01:56:07.700
他不会接受提问的  谢谢
He will not be taking any questions. Thank you.

01:56:11.820 --> 01:56:14.020
自我上次见大家过去好一阵了
Been a while since I was in front of you.

01:56:14.020 --> 01:56:15.950
我这次还是照稿读吧
I figure I'll stick to the cards this time.

01:56:18.890 --> 01:56:19.830
有人猜测
There's been speculation

01:56:19.830 --> 01:56:21.910
我卷入了之前发生在
that I was involved in the events that occurred

01:56:21.910 --> 01:56:23.180
高速和屋顶上的事件
on the freeway and the rooftop...

01:56:23.180 --> 01:56:24.290
抱歉  斯塔克先生
I'm sorry, Mr Stark,

01:56:24.290 --> 01:56:26.150
你真的指望我们相信
but do you honestly expect us to believe that

01:56:26.150 --> 01:56:30.040
那是一个穿战衣的保镖  碰巧出现
that was a bodyguard in a suit that conveniently appeared,

01:56:30.040 --> 01:56:32.820
-尽管你...  -我知道情况让人糊涂
- despite the fact that you... - I know that it's confusing.

01:56:33.260 --> 01:56:35.900
质疑官方说辞是一回事
It is one thing to question the official story,

01:56:35.900 --> 01:56:38.240
但提出疯狂指控  或暗示说
and another thing entirely to make wild accusations,

01:56:38.240 --> 01:56:40.400
我是个超级英雄可是另一码事了
or insinuate that I'm a superhero.

01:56:40.400 --> 01:56:42.080
我可没说你是超级英雄
I never said you were a superhero.

01:56:42.080 --> 01:56:43.640
是吗  那很好
Didn't? Well, good,

01:56:43.640 --> 01:56:47.800
因为那是不着边际  异想天开的
because that would be outlandish and fantastic.

01:56:49.390 --> 01:56:53.040
我显然不是做英雄的料
I'm just not the hero type. Clearly.

01:56:53.210 --> 01:56:56.310
我有一堆性格缺陷
With this laundry list of character defects,

01:56:56.310 --> 01:56:57.760
犯过那么多错误
all the mistakes I've made,

01:56:57.760 --> 01:57:01.240
-还很公开  -照稿读就行
- largely public. - Just stick to the cards, man.

01:57:01.240 --> 01:57:03.150
好  好
Yeah, okay. Yeah.

01:57:05.010 --> 01:57:06.090
事实就是
The truth is

01:57:12.700 --> 01:57:14.060
我就是钢铁侠
I am Iron Man.

02:05:17.380 --> 02:05:18.470
贾维斯
Jarvis!

02:05:18.780 --> 02:05:20.680
欢迎回家  先生
Welcome home, sir.

02:05:23.900 --> 02:05:25.990
"我就是钢铁侠"
"I am Iron Man."

02:05:26.830 --> 02:05:29.560
你以为你是这世上唯一的超级英雄吗
You think you're the only superhero in the world?

02:05:29.790 --> 02:05:30.500
斯塔克先生
Mr Stark,

02:05:30.500 --> 02:05:32.920
你已经成为了更大的宇宙的一部分
you've become part of a bigger universe.

02:05:32.960 --> 02:05:35.250
你只是现在还不知道
You just don't know it yet.

02:05:35.360 --> 02:05:36.540
你是谁
Who the hell are you?

02:05:37.440 --> 02:05:40.200
尼克·弗瑞  神盾局局长
Nick Fury, Director of S.H.I.E.L.D.

02:05:42.170 --> 02:05:44.800
我来跟你谈谈复仇者联盟
I'm here to talk to you about the Avenger Initiative.
